@@option quadlet:subnet

# EXAMPLES

Basic bridge network:

```
[Network]
NetworkName=private0
Subnet=10.10.0.0/16
Gateway=10.10.0.1
```

Enable IPv6 with IPAM driver:

```
[Network]
NetworkName=v6net
Subnet=fd00:dead:beef::/64
IPv6=true
IPAMDriver=host-local
```

